title: 'Dancing with the Stars' requires grit, pain tolerance
text:
> Entertainment 'Dancing with the Stars' requires grit, pain tolerance FILE - In this Nov. 10, 2008 file photo, Olympic gold medalist and contestant on the celebrity dance competition series, "Dancing with the Stars," Misty May-Treanor attends the 2008 Glamour Women of the Year Awards at Carnegie Hall in New York. May-Treanor is one of many contestants who have injured themselves, either on, or rehearsing for the show. (AP Photo/Peter Kramer, File) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
